{"tid":1362494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727係元朗反恐大遊行呀！！","createTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T01:59:37.000Z","uid":287173,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"980c8b92da45e1f0bebc9281908cf43047e7cbb9","tid":1362494,"uid":287173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:49.000Z","msg":"分化原居民同市區居民，邊個最開心？<br />\n <br />\n要反嘅係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警恐合作，攻擊市民</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pseudobiologist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpseudobiologist%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07DyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=0747cce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pseudobiologist/</a><br />\n <br />\n國家恐怖主義（State Terrorism）<br />\n<br />\n現在的香港政府恐怖主義國家。除了縱容恐怖分子襲擊香港人，原來恐怖分子是由警車運送的。是香港政府有分策劃及安排週日的恐怖襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n請各位參與聯署，要求國際制裁香港共產政府。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港是國際的政治提款機。香港政府不單是受到傳媒和香港人的監察，現在還受到別國情報人員的監察。這同時就更加重香港政府的管治成本。<br />\n<br />\n現在的戰爭，就是要否定香港政府的合法性，同時使他們管治不了香港。<br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07DyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=6bfa72a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-07-23/276474\" data-sr-url=\"https